  <brief_title>Evaluation of N1539 Following Major Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Multicenter, Evaluation of the Safety of N1539 Following Major Surgery</official_title>
